oes%20not%20want%20the%20people%20belonging%20to%20SC%2FST%20communities%20to%20get%20quota%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%20her%20party%2C%20if%20voted%20to%20power%2C%20will%20work%20to%20fulfil%20the%20demands%20and%20address%20problems%20of%20the%20region.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20take%20positive%20steps%20with%20regards%20to%20your%20longstanding%20demand%20of%20a%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20bench%20here%20in%20Meerut%20like%20that%20in%20Lucknow%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20central%20government%20has%20not%20been%20paying%20attention%20to%20it%20but%20when%20we%20come%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20we%20will%20take%20positive%20steps%20in%20this%20regard%2C%26quot%3B%20Mayawati%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20how%20her%20government%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20had%20passed%20a%20resolution%20for%20a%20separate%20state%2C%20which%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Centre%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSince%20the%20beginning%2C%20our%20party%20has%20been%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20western%20region%20should%20be%20made%20a%20separate%20state%20for%20better%20development%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20got%20a%20resolution%20passed%20by%20the%20state%20assembly%20and%20sent%20to%20the%20central%20government%20but%20they%20did%20not%20act%20on%20it.%20When%20our%20party%20comes%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20your%20western%20UP%20will%20be%20made%20a%20separate%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20alleged%20that%20the%20quota%20facility%20meant%20for%20the%20Dalits%2C%20adivasis%20(STs)%20and%20OBCs%20in%20government%20jobs%20has%20not%20been%20filled%20up%20in%20the%20country%20for%20years%20and%20the%20quota%20in%20promotions%20for%20the%20SCs%2FSTs%20has%20also%20been%20made%20ineffective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20remind%20the%20members%20of%20the%20SCs%2FSTs%20that%20when%20the%20SP%20was%20in%20power%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20had%20ended%20reservation%20in%20promotions.%20Will%20the%20members%20of%20these%20sections%20give%20even%20a%20single%20vote%20to%20them%20and%20waste%20it%20on%20a%20party%20which%20is%20bent%20upon%20finishing%20their%20reservation.%20The%20SP%20does%20not%20want%20SC%2FST%20people%20to%20get%20full%20benefits%20of%20reservation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20alleged%20that%20when%20an%20amendment%20bill%20for%20reservation%20in%20promotions%20was%20presented%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20SP%20MPs%20had%20torn%20it.%20%26quot%3BWill%20such%20Samajwadi%20Party%20do%20good%20for%20the%20Dalits%20and%20shoshits%20(exploited%20class).%20Not%20only%20this%2C%20the%20districts%2C%20parks%2C%20universities%20that%20we%20(BSP%20government)%20had%20made%20in%20the%20name%20of%20great%20men%20belonging%20to%20these%20sections%20of%20society%20were%20mostly%20changed%20by%20the%20subsequent%20Samajwadi%20Party%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20alleged%20that%20like%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20BJP's%20casteist%20and%20pro-capitalist%20thinking%20and%20policies%20have%20not%20helped%20in%20ensuring%20the%20real%20development%20and%20uplift%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20Dalits%2C%20adivasis%2C%20backwards%2C%20Muslims%20and%20other%20religious%20minorities%20among%20the%20%26quot%3Bsarv%20samaj%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelling%20her%20voters%20that%20in%20these%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20BJP%20and%20their%20supporting%20parties%20have%20to%20be%20stopped%20from%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20she%20alleged%20their%20wrong%20policies%20and%20working%20style%20has%20been%20tried%20by%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20warned%20against%20the%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bsaam%2C%20daam%2C%20dand%2C%20bhed%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20policies%20allegedly%20being%20adopted%20by%20these%20parties%20to%20attain%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeki