to%20refer%20to%20Wayanad%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20this%20not%20an%20insult%20to%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20and%20the%20Constitution%3F%20Is%20this%20not%20meddling%20with%20the%20Constitution%3F%20This%20is%20all%20part%20of%20a%20well-thought-out%20conspiracy%20to%20break%20the%20country.%20Today%2C%20they%20are%20negating%20the%20Constitution%20in%20Goa%2C%20tomorrow%20they%20will%20try%20to%20negate%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20Constitution%20all%20over%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM's%20remarks%20are%20significant%20because%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20wanting%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%20if%20it%20is%20elected%20for%20a%20third%20term.%20This%20was%20also%20stated%20by%20BJP's%20six-time%20MP%20from%20the%20Uttara%20Kannada%20constituency%2C%20Anant%20Hegde%2C%20who%20had%20said%20the%20party%20had%20set%20a%20target%20of%20400%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20for%20the%20NDA%20so%20that%20the%20Constitution%20could%20be%20amended.%20After%20the%20comment%2C%20Mr%20Hegde%20was%20kept%20out%20of%20the%20list%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20the%20Congress'%20charge%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLeave%20aside%20the%20BJP%2C%20even%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20himself%20cannot%20abolish%20the%20Constitution.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Someone%20Else%20Decided%20Destiny'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fernandes%2C%20who%20had%20met%20Mr%20Gandhi%20as%20part%20of%20an%20NGO%2C%20'Goencho%20Away'%2C%20which%20was%20pressing%20for%20dual%20citizenship%20for%20Goans%20who%20have%20opted%20for%20Portuguese%20passports%2C%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20(during%20a%20meeting%20with%20Mr%20Gandhi%20in%20a%20hotel%20near%20Panaji)%20raised%2012%20demands%20before%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20one%20of%20them%20was%20about%20(granting)%20dual%20citizenship.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20asked%20me%20whether%20the%20demand%20was%20constitutional.%20We%20said%20no.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20had%20told%20the%20delegation%20that%20the%20demand%20would%20not%20be%20considered%20if%20it%20was%20not%20constitutional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20explained%20to%20him%20that%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20came%20into%20force%20on%20January%2026%2C%201950.%20When%20Goa%20was%20liberated%20from%20the%20Portuguese%20rule%20in%201961%2C%20you%20(referring%20to%20the%20then%20Central%20government)%20forced%20the%20Constitution%20on%20us.%20We%20were%20not%20included%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Fernandes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20candidate%20said%20he%20recalled%20a%20speech%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20grandfather%2C%20in%20which%20he%20said%20that%20post-liberation%20Goa%20will%20decide%20its%20own%20destiny.%20%26quot%3BBut%20our%20destiny%20was%20decided%20by%20someone%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20PTI)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713876000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F9kjvpcgo_pm-modi-_625x300_23_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-pm-modi-they-want-to-break-country-pm-on-goa-congress-leaders-constitution-remarks-5506080%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seizing%20on%20the%20remarks%20by%20the%20party's%20South%20Goa%20candidate%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20party%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20insulting%20BR%20Ambdekar's%20Constitution%20and%20attempting%20to%20break%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-pm-modi-they-want-to-break-country-pm-on-goa-congress-leaders-constitution-remarks-5506080%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl