%20bulletproof%2C%20it%20is%20not%20waterproof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20buttons%20on%20the%20steering%20wheel%20caused%20a%20five-hour%20computer%20reset%2C%20which%20eventually%20got%20the%20broken-down%20Cybertruck%20operating%20again.%20The%20user%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20(Tesla)%20said%20was%2C%20'It%20is%20a%20known%20issue%20in%20the%20Cybertruck%20that%20when%20you%20do%20a%20screen%20reset%2C%20instead%20of%20resetting%20in%20the%20standard%20two%20minutes%2C%20it%20takes%20five%20hours'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20electric%20car%20manufacturer%20lists%20several%20warnings%20and%20risks%20involved%20with%20washing%20the%20vehicle%20in%20the%20owner's%20manual%20of%20the%20Cybertruck.%20It%20includes%20a%20warning%20not%20to%20wash%20it%20in%20direct%20sunlight%20and%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20avoid%20damaging%20it%20while%20having%20your%20car%20washed.%20As%20per%20the%20outlet%2C%20the%20manual%20states%2C%20%26quot%3BFailure%20to%20put%20Cybertruck%20in%20Car%20Wash%20Mode%20may%20result%20in%20damage%20(for%20example%2C%20to%20the%20charge%20port%20or%20windshield%20wipers).%20Damage%20caused%20by%20car%20washes%20is%20not%20covered%20by%20the%20warranty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20led%20by%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20has%20not%20issued%20a%20comment%20on%20the%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Tesla%20has%20cut%20prices%20by%20nearly%20%242%2C000%20across%20its%20models%20in%20China%2C%20after%20price%20cuts%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20as%20it%20grapples%20with%20falling%20sales%20and%20an%20intensifying%20price%20war%20for%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%2C%20especially%20against%20cheaper%20Chinese%20EVs.%20The%20EV%20maker%20cut%20the%20starting%20price%20of%20the%20revamped%20Model%203%20in%20China%20by%2014%2C000%20yuan%20(%241%2C930)%20to%20231%2C900%20yuan%20(%2432%2C000)%2C%20its%20official%20website%20showed%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20made%20similar%20cuts%20