0They%20do%20not%20analyse%20the%20results%20much.%20Their%20mood%20and%20mood%20swings%20are%20not%20because%20of%20the%20results.%20MI%20is%20a%20bit%20different.%20MI%20mostly%20wants%20to%20win%2C%20and%20their%20culture%20is%20like%20everything%20depends%20on%20winning.%20They%20have%20a%20culture%20of%20%3Cem%3Ejeetna%20hi%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(win%20is%20a%20must).%20Winning%20is%20non-negotiable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rayudu%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLFgdfQxOI3c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStar%20Sports%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20CSK%20and%20MI%20have%20two%20different%20cultures%2C%20but%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20both%20work%20hard.%20I%20feel%20CSK%20has%20a%20much%20better%20environment.%20You%20can%20play%20there%20longer.%20If%20you%20play%20in%20MI%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20%3Cem%3Etoh%20brain%20fatt%20jayega%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Your%20brain%20will%20explode).%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERayudu%20explained%20further%20his%20point%20about%20the%20different%20in%20culture%20in%20MI%20and%20CSK.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20used%20to%20play%20for%20MI%2C%20my%20game%20improved%20a%20lot.%20If%20you%20had%20not%20won%20the%20match%2C%20they%20would%20not%20see%20an%20excuse.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20you%20have%20to%20perform.%20MI%20has%20an%20environment%20where%20you%20keep%20getting%20better%2C%20and%20CSK%20has%20an%20environment%2C%20%3Cem%3EWahaan%20aapko%20better%20bana%20diya%20jaata%20hai%2C%20vo%20bhi%20aaram%20se%3C%2Fem%3E%20(At%20CSK%2C%20you%20are%20made%20better%2C%20and%20that%20too%20without%20any%20hassle)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rayudu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20Rohit%20Sharma%20leave%20Mumbai%20Indians%20after%20IPL%202024%3F%20That's%20one%20speculation%20which%20is%20currently%20ruling%20the%20spectators'%20mind.%20Before%20the%20IPL%202025%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20mega%20auction.%20The%20mega%20auction%20often%20sees%20the%20team%20