0while%20his%20wife%20Sriratna%20Koneru%20has%20Rs%202%2C343.78%20crore%20worth%20assets%20and%20children%20have%20nearly%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20press%20release%20by%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20had%20earlier%20said%2C%20former%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Kamal%20Nath's%20son%20Nakul%20Nath%20topped%20the%20richest%20contestants%20list%20in%20the%20Phase-I%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20held%20on%20April%2019%2C%20with%20nearly%20Rs%20717%20crore%20worth%20of%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandra%20Sekhar's%20family%20has%20a%20liability%20of%20Rs%201%2C138%20crore%20to%20JP%20Morgan%20Chase%20Bank%20of%20USA%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Line%20of%20Credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Burripalem%20village%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20to%20working%20as%20physician%20teacher%20at%20Johns%20Hopkins%20University%20-%20Sinai%20Hospital%20to%20founding%20UWorld%20(online%20learning%20and%20study%20resources%20platform)%2C%20Chandra%20Sekhar's%20journey%20has%20been%20fascinating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Doctor-Entrepreneur-Politician%20completed%20his%20MBBS%20at%20NTR%20University%20of%20Health%20Sciences%20Vijayawada%20in%201999%20and%20pursued%20MD%20(Internal%20Medicine)%20from%20Geisinger%20Medical%20Center%20in%20Danville%2C%20Pennsylvania%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20secured%2027th%20rank%20among%2060%2C000%20students%20who%20took%20the%20EAMCET%20medical%20entrance%20examination%20(MBBS)%20in%20the%20state%20which%20was%20considered%20the%20most%20competitive%20examination%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandra%20Sekhar%20with%20an%20interest%20in%20public%20service%2C%20has%20been%20working%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20TDP's%20NRI%20wing%20since%202010%20to%20support%20several%20welfare%20programmes%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20desired%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20from%20Narasaraopet%20segment%20in%202014%2C%20TDP%20allotted%20the%20ticket%20to%20R%20Sambasiva%20Rao%20due%20to%20political%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20filing%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20he%20declared%20Rs%20605.57%20crore%20as%20per%20US%20Tax%20Cycle%20Year%20January%202022%20to%20December%202022%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20investments%20and%20shares%20in%20several%20US-based%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20possesses%20luxury%20cars%20such%20as%20Rolls%20Royce%20Ghost%2C%20Mercedes%20Benz%20and%20Tesla%20in%20the%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChnadra%20Sekhar%20will%20take%20on%20YSR%20Congress%20Party's%20K%20Venkata%20Rosaiah%20in%20the%20elections.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713871140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fs9qg2r6o_pemmasani-chandra-sekhar_625x300_22_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-rs-5-785-crore-assets-this-lok-sabha-contestant-is-wealthiest-so-far-5504033%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TDP's%20candidate%20for%20Guntur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20P%20Chandra%20Sekhar%20has%20captured%20headlines%20after%20he%20declared%20his%20family%20assets%20-%20both%20movable%20and%20immovable%20-%20at%20Rs%205%2C785%20crore%2C%20in%20his%20election%20affidavit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-rs-5-785-crore-assets-this-lok-sabha-contestant-is-wealthiest-so-far-5504033%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-rs-5-785-crore-assets-this-lok-sabha-contestant-is-wealthiest-so-far-5504033%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-rs-5-785-crore-assets-this-lok-sabha-contestant-is-wealthiest-so-far-5504033%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2