robability%20of%20danger'%20that%20the%20patient%20will%20have%20an%20imminent%20episode%2C%26quot%3B%20Jorge%20Goncalves%2C%20from%20the%20Luxembourg%20Centre%20for%20Systems%20Biomedicine%20(LCSB)%2C%20University%20of%20Luxembourg%2C%20and%20the%20study's%20corresponding%20author%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20approaching%20atrial%20fibrillation%2C%20the%20probability%20increases%20until%20it%20crosses%20a%20specific%20threshold%2C%20providing%20an%20early%20warning%2C%20Goncalves%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20of%20low%20computational%20cost%2C%20the%20AI-model%20is%20%26quot%3Bideal%20for%20integration%20into%20wearable%20technologies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researchers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20devices%20can%20be%20used%20by%20patients%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20so%20our%20results%20open%20possibilities%20for%20the%20development%20of%20real-time%20monitoring%20and%20early%20warnings%20from%20comfortable%20wearable%20devices%2C%26quot%3B%20study%20author%20Arthur%20Montanari%2C%20an%20LCSB%20researcher%2C%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713870240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Forhm5fbg_heart-rate-generic-cardiac-monitor-generic-hospital-generic-pixabay_625x300_23_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fai-model-developed-to-predict-cardiac-irregularity-30-minutes-before-onset-study-5504434%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Researchers%20have%20developed%20a%20new%20AI-based%20model%20that%20can%20predict%20irregular%20heartbeat%2C%20or%20cardiac%20arrhythmia%2C%20about%2030%20minutes%20before%20its%20onset.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fai-model-developed-to-predict-cardiac-irregularity-30-minutes-before-onset-study-5504434%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fai-model-developed-to-predict-cardiac-irregularity-30-minutes-before-onset-study-5504434%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fai-model-developed-to-predict-cardiac-irregularity-30-minutes-before-onset-study-5504434%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMy%2090-Second%20Speech%20Created%20Panic%20In%20Congress%2C%20INDIA%20Bloc%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20debate%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20remarks%20that%20%26quot%3BCongress%20wants%20to%20snatch%20women's%20Mangalsutra%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20reiterated%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20had%20put%20the%20truth%20before%20the%20country%20that%20Congress%20is%20hatching%20a%20deep%20conspiracy%20to%20snatch%20your%20property%20and%20distribute%20it%20to%20its%20special%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20public%20meeting%20here%20today%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20his%20speech%20had%20created%20panic%20in%20the%20entire%20Congress%20and%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20came%20to%20Rajasthan%20the%20day%20before%20yesterday%2C%20I%20had%20presented%20some%20truths%20before%20the%20country%20in%20my%2090-second%20speech.%20This%20has%20created%20panic%20in%20the%20entire%20Congress%20and%20INDI%20alliance.%20I%20had%20put%20the%20truth%20before%20the%20country%20that%20Congress%20is%20hatching%20a%20deep%20conspiracy%20to%20snatch%20your%20property%20and%20distribute%20it%20to%20its%20special%20people.%20I%20exposed%20their%20vote%20bank%20and%20appeasement%20politics.%20After%20all%2C%20why%20is%20Congress%20so%20afraid%20of%20the%20truth%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20asked%20what%20would%20have%20happened%20if%20there%20was%20a%20Congress%20government%20at%20the%20centre%20after%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202014%2C%20you%20allowed%20Modi%20to%20serve%20in%20Delhi.%20Then%20the%20country%20made%20decisions%20that%20no%20one%20had%20even%20imagined.%20But%20think%20about%20what%20would%20have%20happened%20even%20after%202014%20and%20even%20today%20if%20there%20was%20a%20Congress%20government%20in%20Delhi.%20Had%20Congress%20been%20there%2C%20stones%20would%20have%20been%20pelted%20at%20our%20forces%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20even%20today.%20Had%20Congress%20been%20there%2C%20the%20enemies%20would%20have%20come%20from%20across%20the%20border.%20Had%20Congress%20been%20there%2C%20neither%20One%20Rank%20One%20Pension%20would%20have%20been%20implemented%20for%20our%20soldiers%20nor%20would%20our%20ex-servicemen%20have%20received%20Rs%201%20lakh%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20sharpening%20his%20attacks%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20thinking%20of%20Congress%20has%20always%20been%20of%20appeasement%20and%20vote%20bank%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20the%20Congress%20government%20was%20formed%20at%20the%20Centre%20in%202004%2C%20its%20first%20task%20was%20to%20reduce%20the%20reservation%20for%20SC%2FST%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20give%20reservation%20to%20Muslims.%20This%20was%20a%20pilot%20project%2C%20which%20Congress%20wanted%20to%20try%20in%20the%20entire%20country.%20Between%202004%20and%202010%2C%20Congress%20tried%20to%20implement%20Muslim%20reservations%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20four%20times.%20But%20due%20to%20legal%20hurdles%20and%20the%20awareness%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20it%20could%20not%20fulfil%20its%20plans%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20is%20completely%20against%20it.%20The%20right%20of%20reservation%20which%20Baba%20Saheb%20gave%20to%20Dalits%2C%20backward%20classes%20and%20tribals%2C%20Congress%20and%20INDI%20Alliance%20wanted%20to%20give%20it%20to%20Muslims%20based%20on%20religion.%20Amidst%20these%20conspiracies%20of%20Congress%2C%20Modi%20is%20today%20guaranteeing%20you%20from%20an%20open%20platform%20that%20reservations%20for%20Dalits%2C%20backward%20classes%20and%20tribals%20will%20neither%20be%20ended%20nor%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20be%20divided%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion.%20This%20is%20Modi's%20guarantee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713869400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F3drvci2o_pm-modi-1200-_625x300_23_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmy-90-second-speech-created-panic-in-congress-india-bloc-pm-modi-5503549%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20debate%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20remarks%20that%20%26quot%3BCongress%20wants%20to%20snatch%20women's%20Mangalsutra%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20reiterated%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20had%20put%20the%20truth%20before%20the%20country%20that%20Congress%20is%20hatching%20a%20deep%20conspiracy%20to%20snatch%20your%20property%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmy-90-second-speech-created-panic-in-congress-india-bloc-pm-modi-5503549%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmy-90-second-speech-created-panic-in-congress-india-bloc-pm-modi-5503549%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmy-90-second-speech-created-panic-in-congress-india-bloc-pm-modi-5503549%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tesla%20Fires%20Entire%20US%20%26quot%3BGrowth%20Team%26quot%3B%20Built%20Just%204%20Months%20Ago%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETesla%20slashed%20a%20newly%20formed%20marketing%20team%20as%20part%20of%20companywide%20layoffs%2C%20reversing%20course%20from%20a%20traditional%20advertising%20push%20that%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Elon%20Musk%20greenlighted%20less%20than%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20US%20%26quot%3Bgrowth%20content%26quot%3B%20team%2C%20a%20group%20of%20about%2040%20employees%20overseen%20by%20senior%20manager%20Alex%20Ingram%2C%20was%20eliminated%20in%20the%20ongoing%20job%20cuts%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIngram%20and%20Jorge%20Milburn%2C%20who%20led%20the%20global%20team%2C%20were%20dismissed%2C%20they%20said.%20The%20company%20still%20has%20a%20small%20number%20of%20marketing%20staff%20in%20Europe%2C%20one%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20significant%20layoffs%20in%20Tesla's%20design%20studio%20and%20staff%20located%20in%20Hawthorne%2C%20California%2C%20said%20the%20people%2C%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20discussing%20private%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20responding%20to%20Bloomberg's%20report%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20wrote%20of%20the%20content%20team's%20work%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20ads%20were%20far%20too%20generic%20-%20could've%20been%20any%20car.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cuts%20mark%20a%20pullback%20from%20Tesla's%20nascent%20advertising%20initiatives.%20The%20automaker%20had%20long%20eschewed%20television%2C%20radio%2C%20print%2C%20or%20online%20ads%20-%20and%20had%20built%20a%20formidable%20brand%20largely%20through%20word-of-mouth%20-%20before%20Musk%20said%20last%20year%20that%20Tesla%20would%20%26quot%3Btry%20a%20little%20advertising%20and%20see%20how%20it%20goes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIngram%20started%20building%20the%20growth%20team%20about%20four%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestors%20have%20increasingly%20called%20on%20Musk%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20marketing%20as%20global%20EV%20sales%20growth%20has%20slowed%20and%20