2%26quot%3BVote%20For%20BJP%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Goons%20Will%20Be%20Hung%20Upside%20Down%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20do%20not%20have%20the%20guts%20to%20touch%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20today%2C%20assuring%20that%20all%20Hindu%20refugees%20will%20get%20citizenship%20under%20the%20new%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20was%20addressing%20a%20rally%20at%20Karandighi%20in%20Bengal's%20Uttar%20Dinajpur%20district%20to%20bolster%20support%20for%20BJP%20candidate%20from%20Raiganj%20Kartik%20Paul.%20The%20Raiganj%20seat%20was%20won%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%202019.%20Trinamool%20has%20fielded%20Krishna%20Kalyani%2C%20an%20MLA%2C%20from%20the%20north%20Bengal%20seat.%20Raiganj%20votes%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20the%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20cannot%20stop%20infiltration%20into%20the%20border%20state.%20%26quot%3BCan%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20stop%20infiltration%3F%20She%20cannot.%20Only%20(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra)%20Modiji%20can%20stop%20infiltration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20gave%20us%2018%20seats%20last%20time.%20Modiji%20gave%20Ram%20Mandir.%20Give%20us%2035%20seats%20this%20time%2C%20we%20will%20stop%20infiltration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20row%2C%20which%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20big%20talking%20point%20in%20Bengal%20this%20election%20season.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20allowed%20women%20to%20be%20tortured%20so%20that%20her%20votebank%20is%20not%20affected.%20The%20High%20Court%20intervened%20and%20today%20the%20accused%20are%20in%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%20The%20island%20in%20Bengal's%20North%2024%20Parganas%20had%20made%20national%20headlines%20after%20local%20Trinamool%20leaders%20were%20accused%20of%20land%20grab%2C%20extortion%20and%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20also%20brought%20up%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court's%20order%20scrapping%20about%2025%2C000%20appointments%20of%20government%20school%20staff%20over%20alleged%20irregularities.%20%26quot%3BRs%2010%20lakh%20to%2015%20lakh%20were%20paid%20for%20each%20job.%2051%20crore%20rupees%20were%20recovered%20from%20(former%20Bengal%20minister)%20Partha%20Chatterjee's%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMamata%20Banerjee%20came%20to%20power%20on%20the%20slogan%20of%20Maa%2C%20Maati%2C%20Manush.%20In%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Maa%20was%20tortured%2C%20Maati%20was%20given%20to%20Bangladeshi%20infiltrators%20and%20Manush%20have%20been%20suffering%20due%20to%20corruption%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%20%26quot%3BVote%20for%20BJP%20and%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20goondas%20will%20be%20hung%20upside%20down%20and%20straightened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20of%20corruption%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%20at%20TMC%20leaders'%20houses.%20Those%20who%20stayed%20in%20thatched%20roof%20houses%20today%20own%20four-storeyed%20houses%2C%20roam%20around%20in%20cars.%20This%20is%20your%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20promised%20that%20the%20Centre%20will%20set%20up%20an%20AIIMS%20in%20north%20Bengal%20if%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20BJP%20returns%20to%20power.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20planned%20an%20AIIMS%20in%20Raiganj.%20Mamata%20didi%20blocked%20it.%20This%20is%20Modiji's%20guarantee.%20Give%20us%2030%20seats%2C%20we%20will%20start%20work%20on%20north%20Bengal's%20first%20AIIMS.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20back-to-back%20rallies%20in%20Raiganj%20and%20Kumarganj%20yesterday%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20panic%20mode%20after%20sensing%20defeat%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20polling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFear%20and%20panic%20have%20gripped%20the%20BJP.%20After%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20polling%20in%20nearly%20100%20seats%20across%20the%20country%2C%20they%20have%20sensed%20defeat.%20That%20is%20why%20they%20are%20making%20baseless%20statements.%20The%20rout%20of%20the%20saffron%20camp%20is%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0On%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20ploy%20to%20malign%20us%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20she%20will%20not%20allow%20the%20citizenship%20law%20to%20be%20implemented.%20%26quot%3BThe%20CAA%20is%20a%20trap%20to%20turn%20legal%20citizens%20into%20foreigners.%20Once%20you%20implement%20CAA%2C%20NRC%20will%20follow.%20We%20will%20allow%20neither%20CAA%20nor%20NRC%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20If%20you%20apply%2C%20you%20will%20be%20designated%20as%20a%20foreigner%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713866160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F01v77ok_amit-shah-mamata-banerjee_625x300_23_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-2024-lok-sabha-election-mamata-banerjee-vote-for-bjp-mamata-banerjees-goons-will-be-hung-upside-down-amit-shah-5504673%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20do%20not%20have%20the%20guts%20to%20touch%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20today%2C%20assuring%20that%20all%20Hindu%20refugees%20will%20get%20citizenship%20under%20the%20new%20law.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-2024-lok-sabha-election-mamata-banerjee-vote-for-bjp-mamata-banerjees-goons-will-be-hung-upside-down-amit-shah-5504673%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-2024-lok-sabha-election-mamata-banerjee-vote-for-bjp-mamata-ba